qwirkle.client

Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • qwirkle.client.Client
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Client
extends java.util.Observable
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Client class that can work standalone. It can connect to a qwirkle server and using the protocol communicate. It will try to connect over SSL, it that fails it falls back to a regular socket. This client runs on a separate thread.
